{
  "title": "Application Registration for Data & More Compliance Solution (DMCS)",
  "slug": "rights-overview",
  "categorySlug": "data-sources",
  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">Application Registration for Data &amp; More Compliance Solution (DMCS)</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">The Application Permission includes authentication for Graph, Exchange Online and SharePoint Online / OneDrive. </h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><strong>Quick Overview of API Permissions</strong><br><br><strong>Step-by-Step Guide</strong><br>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#Application_Registration\" rel=\"noopener\">Application Registration</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#Redirect\" rel=\"noopener\">Redirect URL&nbsp;</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#API-permissions\" rel=\"noopener\">API Permissions</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#Keys\" rel=\"noopener\">Keys</a><br><br></li>\n</ul>\n<hr><br>\n<h3><strong>Quick Overview of API Permissions using Graph Application Permissions</strong></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Rights for PoC</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul>\n<li>User.Read (AD)</li>\n<li>User.Read.All (AD)</li>\n<li>Directory.Read.All (AD)</li>\n<li>Mail.Read (Exchange Online)</li>\n<li>Mail.Send (Sends Reports)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Return URL for PoC</strong><br>&nbsp;https://signup.dataandmore.com/api/authorize_redirect</p>\n<p>_____________________________________________</p>\n<p><strong>Rights for Production</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul>\n<li>Mail.ReadWrite (Exchange Online)</li>\n<li>MailboxSettings.ReadWrite (Outlook Categories) * Optional</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul>\n<li>Contacts.Read (Extract Known Persons) * Optional</li>\n<li>Files.ReadWrite.All (OneDrive)</li>\n<li>Sites.FullControl.All (SharePoint)</li>\n<li>Sites.ReadWrite.All (SharePoint)</li>\n<li>InformationProtectionPolicy.Read.All (CoPilot Protection)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<a id=\"Redirect\" data-hs-anchor=\"true\"></a>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"//support.dataandmore.com/knowledge/enforce_ad\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Redirect URL&nbsp; Azure AD Authentication</a></strong><br>We need to add a 'Redirect URL' and the platform have to be 'Web' .&nbsp;<br><br><img alt=\"BlZ4O\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"200\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/BlZ4O.png?width=688&amp;height=200&amp;name=BlZ4O.png\" width=\"688\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/BlZ4O.png?width=344&amp;height=100&amp;name=BlZ4O.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/BlZ4O.png?width=688&amp;height=200&amp;name=BlZ4O.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/BlZ4O.png?width=1032&amp;height=300&amp;name=BlZ4O.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/BlZ4O.png?width=1376&amp;height=400&amp;name=BlZ4O.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/BlZ4O.png?width=1720&amp;height=500&amp;name=BlZ4O.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/BlZ4O.png?width=2064&amp;height=600&amp;name=BlZ4O.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"><br>\n<ul>\n<li>\"the primary server domain\" + \"<em>/api/auth/ad/login/authorized</em>\"</li>\n<li>\n<p>So if your server domain is: <em>https://gdpr.dataandmore.com</em> then redirect URL should be:</p>\n<p><em>https://gdpr.dataandmore.com<strong>/api/auth/ad/login/authorized</strong></em></p>\n</li>\n<li><em><strong>And a universal return URL for PoC</strong></em><br>https://signup.dataandmore.com/api/authorize_redirect</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong><a href=\"//support.dataandmore.com/knowledge/how-to-set-up-an-application-registration-for-exchange-online\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Office 365 Exchange Online Application Permission</a></strong></h3>\n<p>This application permission is based on EWS and is only in-use if OnlineArchive are to be scanned.</p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul>\n<li>full_access_as_app<br><br><br></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n<div class=\"hs-callout-type-caution\" data-hs-callout-type=\"caution\">\n<p>Send the applications id (client id) to support@dataandmore.com</p>\n<p>Send the secret value&nbsp; (NOT&nbsp; secret id) directly to your contact in Data &amp; More</p>\n</div>\n<a id=\"Step-by-Step\" data-hs-anchor=\"true\"></a>\n<h3><strong>Step-by-Step Guide</strong></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<a id=\"Application_Registration\" data-hs-anchor=\"true\"></a>\n<h3><strong>1. Application Registration</strong></h3>\n<p>Go to portal.azure.com and log in with the global admin of your 365 domain. Search and select <em>App Registration</em>.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2022-10-19 at 14.33.35\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"242\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.33.35.png?width=688&amp;height=242&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.33.35.png\" width=\"688\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.33.35.png?width=344&amp;height=121&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.33.35.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.33.35.png?width=688&amp;height=242&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.33.35.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.33.35.png?width=1032&amp;height=363&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.33.35.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.33.35.png?width=1376&amp;height=484&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.33.35.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.33.35.png?width=1720&amp;height=605&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.33.35.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.33.35.png?width=2064&amp;height=726&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.33.35.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>You’ll see a list of all your registered applications and a few options at the top. Select <em>New registration.</em></p>\n<p><em><img alt=\"Screenshot 2022-10-19 at 14.34.57\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"129\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.34.57.png?width=688&amp;height=129&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.34.57.png\" width=\"688\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.34.57.png?width=344&amp;height=65&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.34.57.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.34.57.png?width=688&amp;height=129&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.34.57.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.34.57.png?width=1032&amp;height=194&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.34.57.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.34.57.png?width=1376&amp;height=258&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.34.57.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.34.57.png?width=1720&amp;height=323&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.34.57.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.34.57.png?width=2064&amp;height=387&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.34.57.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>When creating new app registration, you’ll need to name it, choose who can use it and enter a redirect URL.&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Redirect URL - \"the primary server domain\" + \"/api/auth/ad/login/authorized\"</li>\n</ul>\n<p>So if your server domain is: https://gdpr.dataandmore.com the redirect URL should be:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://gdpr.dataandmore.com/api/auth/ad/login/authorized\">https://gdpr.dataandmore.com/api/auth/ad/login/authorized</a></p>\n<p>Click on the <em>Register</em> button on the bottom left.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2022-10-19 at 14.42.58\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"433\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.42.58.png?width=688&amp;height=433&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.42.58.png\" width=\"688\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.42.58.png?width=344&amp;height=217&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.42.58.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.42.58.png?width=688&amp;height=433&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.42.58.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.42.58.png?width=1032&amp;height=650&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.42.58.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.42.58.png?width=1376&amp;height=866&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.42.58.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.42.58.png?width=1720&amp;height=1083&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.42.58.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.42.58.png?width=2064&amp;height=1299&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.42.58.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>When app registration is created, you’ll see the <em>Overview</em> page with all the details such as <em>Name, Client ID, Tenant ID, Object ID</em> and so on.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<a id=\"API-permissions\" data-hs-anchor=\"true\"></a>\n<h3><strong>2. API permissions</strong></h3>\n<p>Go to <em>API Permissions</em> which can be found on the left side.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2022-10-19 at 15.15.00\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"230\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.15.00.png?width=688&amp;height=230&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.15.00.png\" width=\"688\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.15.00.png?width=344&amp;height=115&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.15.00.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.15.00.png?width=688&amp;height=230&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.15.00.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.15.00.png?width=1032&amp;height=345&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.15.00.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.15.00.png?width=1376&amp;height=460&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.15.00.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.15.00.png?width=1720&amp;height=575&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.15.00.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.15.00.png?width=2064&amp;height=690&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.15.00.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Click on <em>Add a permission.</em></p>\n<p><em><img alt=\"Screenshot 2022-10-19 at 15.17.00\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"201\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.17.00.png?width=688&amp;height=201&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.17.00.png\" width=\"688\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.17.00.png?width=344&amp;height=101&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.17.00.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.17.00.png?width=688&amp;height=201&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.17.00.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.17.00.png?width=1032&amp;height=302&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.17.00.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.17.00.png?width=1376&amp;height=402&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.17.00.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.17.00.png?width=1720&amp;height=503&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.17.00.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.17.00.png?width=2064&amp;height=603&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.17.00.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Click on <strong>Microsoft Graph</strong> and select <em>Application permissions</em></p>\n<p><em><img alt=\"Screenshot 2022-10-19 at 15.19.50\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"225\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.19.50.png?width=688&amp;height=225&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.19.50.png\" width=\"688\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.19.50.png?width=344&amp;height=113&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.19.50.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.19.50.png?width=688&amp;height=225&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.19.50.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.19.50.png?width=1032&amp;height=338&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.19.50.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.19.50.png?width=1376&amp;height=450&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.19.50.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.19.50.png?width=1720&amp;height=563&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.19.50.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.19.50.png?width=2064&amp;height=675&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.19.50.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></em></p>\n<p>Add the following permissions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>User.Read (AD)</li>\n<li>User.Read.All (AD)</li>\n<li>Directory.Read.All (AD)</li>\n<li>Mail.ReadWrite (Exchange Online)</li>\n<li>Mail.Send (Sends Reports)</li>\n<li>Contacts.Read (Extract Known Persons)</li>\n<li>MailboxSettings.ReadWrite (Outlook Categories)</li>\n<li>Files.ReadWrite.All (OneDrive)</li>\n<li>Sites.FullControl.All (SharePoint)</li>\n<li>Sites.ReadWrite.All (SharePoint)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><br></em>Click on<em> Add permissions.</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>After adding Microsoft Graph API permission, you need to add one more - <strong>Office 365 Exchange Online.&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p>To do that, again click on <em>Add a permission, </em>but this time go to <strong>APIs my organization uses</strong> tab and search for <em>Office 365 Exchange Online</em>.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2022-10-19 at 15.34.28\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"410\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.34.28.png?width=688&amp;height=410&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.34.28.png\" width=\"688\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.34.28.png?width=344&amp;height=205&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.34.28.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.34.28.png?width=688&amp;height=410&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.34.28.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.34.28.png?width=1032&amp;height=615&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.34.28.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.34.28.png?width=1376&amp;height=820&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.34.28.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.34.28.png?width=1720&amp;height=1025&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.34.28.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.34.28.png?width=2064&amp;height=1230&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.34.28.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Click on <em>Application permissions</em>, select full_access_as_app and click on <em>Add permissions</em> button.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2022-10-19 at 15.38.24\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"525\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.38.24.png?width=688&amp;height=525&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.38.24.png\" width=\"688\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.38.24.png?width=344&amp;height=263&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.38.24.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.38.24.png?width=688&amp;height=525&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.38.24.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.38.24.png?width=1032&amp;height=788&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.38.24.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.38.24.png?width=1376&amp;height=1050&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.38.24.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.38.24.png?width=1720&amp;height=1313&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.38.24.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.38.24.png?width=2064&amp;height=1575&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.38.24.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The last step is to Grant admin consent for the added permissions. To do that, simply click on <em>Grant admin consent</em> on the top of the table and confirm the action in the pop up window.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2022-10-19 at 15.42.57\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"341\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.42.57.png?width=688&amp;height=341&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.42.57.png\" width=\"688\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.42.57.png?width=344&amp;height=171&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.42.57.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.42.57.png?width=688&amp;height=341&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.42.57.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.42.57.png?width=1032&amp;height=512&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.42.57.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.42.57.png?width=1376&amp;height=682&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.42.57.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.42.57.png?width=1720&amp;height=853&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.42.57.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.42.57.png?width=2064&amp;height=1023&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.42.57.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>If you successfully did that, your table should look like this:</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2022-10-19 at 15.44.23\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"346\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.44.23.png?width=688&amp;height=346&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.44.23.png\" width=\"688\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.44.23.png?width=344&amp;height=173&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.44.23.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.44.23.png?width=688&amp;height=346&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.44.23.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.44.23.png?width=1032&amp;height=519&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.44.23.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.44.23.png?width=1376&amp;height=692&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.44.23.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.44.23.png?width=1720&amp;height=865&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.44.23.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.44.23.png?width=2064&amp;height=1038&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.44.23.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></p>\n<a id=\"Keys\" data-hs-anchor=\"true\"></a>\n<h3><strong>3. Keys</strong></h3>\n<p>If you go to the <em>Overview</em> page of your app registration, you'll see all the details such as <em>Name, Client ID, Tenant ID, Object ID</em> and so on.&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"hs-callout-type-warning\" data-hs-callout-type=\"warning\">\n<p>You need to provide Data &amp; More with: Client ID, Tenant ID and Secret Value.&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>Client ID</em> and <em>Tenant ID</em> can be found on the <em>Overview</em> page.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2022-10-19 at 14.49.10\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"283\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.49.10.png?width=688&amp;height=283&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.49.10.png\" width=\"688\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.49.10.png?width=344&amp;height=142&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.49.10.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.49.10.png?width=688&amp;height=283&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.49.10.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.49.10.png?width=1032&amp;height=425&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.49.10.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.49.10.png?width=1376&amp;height=566&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.49.10.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.49.10.png?width=1720&amp;height=708&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.49.10.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.49.10.png?width=2064&amp;height=849&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2014.49.10.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>To get <em>Secret Value</em>, you need to go to <em>Certificates &amp; secrets </em>on the left side and click on <em>New client secret</em>.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2022-10-19 at 15.03.11\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"262\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.03.11.png?width=688&amp;height=262&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.03.11.png\" width=\"688\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.03.11.png?width=344&amp;height=131&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.03.11.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.03.11.png?width=688&amp;height=262&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.03.11.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.03.11.png?width=1032&amp;height=393&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.03.11.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.03.11.png?width=1376&amp;height=524&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.03.11.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.03.11.png?width=1720&amp;height=655&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.03.11.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.03.11.png?width=2064&amp;height=786&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.03.11.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2022-10-19 at 15.05.55\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"827\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.05.55.png?width=688&amp;height=827&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.05.55.png\" width=\"688\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.05.55.png?width=344&amp;height=414&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.05.55.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.05.55.png?width=688&amp;height=827&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.05.55.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.05.55.png?width=1032&amp;height=1241&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.05.55.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.05.55.png?width=1376&amp;height=1654&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.05.55.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.05.55.png?width=1720&amp;height=2068&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.05.55.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.05.55.png?width=2064&amp;height=2481&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.05.55.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></p>\n<p>Add a client secret description and when will it expire. After that, click on <em>Add.</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>When a client secret is created, you should see it on the list with all the details. Secret value can be found here and you need to copy it while you are on this page.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Screenshot 2022-10-19 at 15.12.10\" class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"143\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.12.10.png?width=688&amp;height=143&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.12.10.png\" width=\"688\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.12.10.png?width=344&amp;height=72&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.12.10.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.12.10.png?width=688&amp;height=143&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.12.10.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.12.10.png?width=1032&amp;height=215&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.12.10.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.12.10.png?width=1376&amp;height=286&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.12.10.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.12.10.png?width=1720&amp;height=358&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.12.10.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.12.10.png?width=2064&amp;height=429&amp;name=Screenshot%202022-10-19%20at%2015.12.10.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"hs-callout-type-warning\" data-hs-callout-type=\"warning\">\n<p><strong>IMPORTANT:</strong> Client secret values cannot be viewed, except for immediately after creation. Be sure to save the secret when created before leaving the page.</p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
  "sourceUrl": "https://support.dataandmore.com/en/knowledge/rights-overview"
}